name: 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐆𝐨𝐝
description:
She is worshipped as a principal aspect of the mother goddess Devi and is one of the most popular and widely revered among Indian divinities. She is associated with protection, strength, motherhood, destruction and wars.
Her legend centres around combating evils and demonic forces that threaten peace, prosperity, and Dharma the power of good over evi
Rendered in Blender using Cycles and tweaked in photoshop ( adding additional textures, particles and candle light. )
